你能够调用以下的API:
[['Email.send', {'name': 'Email.send', 'description': 'send email', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'address', 'description': 'the email address to send', 'type': 'STRING'}, {'name': 'title', 'description': 'title of email, not NULL', 'type': 'STRING'}], 'optional_parameters': [{'name': 'body', 'description': 'the content of the email', 'type': 'STRING'}, {'name': 'attachment', 'description': 'path of the attachment file', 'type': 'STRING'}], 'return_data': [{'name': 'state', 'description': 'the state of sending email'}]}], ['FinancialInstitution.get_data_protection_policy', {'name': 'FinancialInstitution.get_data_protection_policy', 'description': 'This function retrieves the data protection policy of a financial institution given its name.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'institution_name', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The name of the financial institution.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'policy_content', 'description': 'The content of the data protection policy.'}]}], ['FinancialInstitution.analyze_policy_compliance', {'name': 'FinancialInstitution.analyze_policy_compliance', 'description': 'This function analyzes the compliance of a given data protection policy.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'policy_content', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The content of the data protection policy.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'compliance_analysis', 'description': 'The analysis result of the policy compliance.'}]}], ['FinancialInstitution.get_data_breach_records', {'name': 'FinancialInstitution.get_data_breach_records', 'description': 'This function retrieves the data breach records of a financial institution within a specified time period.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'institution_name', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The name of the financial institution.'}, {'name': 'time_period', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The time period for which to retrieve the records.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'breach_records', 'description': 'The data breach records within the specified time period.'}]}], ['FinancialInstitution.evaluate_data_protection_level', {'name': 'FinancialInstitution.evaluate_data_protection_level', 'description': 'This function evaluates the overall data protection level of a financial institution based on compliance analysis and data breach records.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'compliance_analysis', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The compliance analysis result.'}, {'name': 'breach_records', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The data breach records.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'evaluation_result', 'description': 'The overall evaluation of the data protection level.'}]}]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `api1` 并传入 `arg1` 和 `arg2`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "api1",
    "args": "{'arg1': 'value1', 'arg2': 'value2', ...}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
